      • formatQuery

        protected String formatQuery(String query)
        Callback method to allow alternating given query for logging. Subclass can override this method to change the given query. For example, it can call BasicFormatterImpl in hibernate to format the query.
        Parameters:
        query - a query to format
        Returns:
        formatted query
        Since:
        1.4.1
